&lt;p&gt;Total distance covered by Mohan daily = 4&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 200&amp;nbsp;m = 800&amp;nbsp;m&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;there4; The total distance covered by Mohan daily is 800 m.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

