questions.explanation:
&lt;meta charset=&quot;UTF-8&quot;&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0&quot;&gt;
&lt;title&gt;&lt;/title&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;Concept:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The mode of a data set is the value that appears most frequently.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Formula Used:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Mode of grouped data is given by:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Mode = L + [(f&lt;sub&gt;1&lt;/sub&gt; - f&lt;sub&gt;0&lt;/sub&gt;) / (2f&lt;sub&gt;1&lt;/sub&gt; - f&lt;sub&gt;0&lt;/sub&gt; - f&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt;)] &amp;times; h&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Where,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;L = Lower boundary of the modal class&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;f&lt;sub&gt;1&lt;/sub&gt; = Frequency of the modal class&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;f&lt;sub&gt;0&lt;/sub&gt; = Frequency of the class preceding the modal class&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;f&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt; = Frequency of the class succeeding the modal class&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;h = Class size&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;From the table, the modal class is 6 - 8 as it has the highest frequency (12).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; L = 6&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; f&lt;sub&gt;1&lt;/sub&gt; = 12&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; f&lt;sub&gt;0&lt;/sub&gt; = 8 (frequency of the class 4 - 6)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; f&lt;sub&gt;2&lt;/sub&gt; = 6 (frequency of the class 8 - 10)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; h = 2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Using the formula:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Mode = 6 + [(12 - 8) / (2 &amp;times; 12 - 8 - 6)] &amp;times; 2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Mode = 6 + [4 / (24 - 14)] &amp;times; 2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Mode = 6 + [4 / 10] &amp;times; 2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Mode = 6 + 0.4 &amp;times; 2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Mode = 6 + 0.8&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; Mode = 6.8&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;there4; The mode of the data is 6.8.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;Formula used :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;Mean = sum of all values in the set/Number of values&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;Median = Middle value in the data set &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;Calculations :&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;Sum of all values = 23 + 31 + 43 + 37 + 51 + 61 + a + 32 + 23 + 27 + 19&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt; 347 + a&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;Number of values = 11&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;According to the question&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;Mean = 33&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt; (347 + a)/11 = 33&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt; 347 + a = 363&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt;&amp;rArr;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; &quot;&gt; a = 16&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Arranged data set = (16, 19, 23, 23, 27, 31, 32, 37, 43, 51, 61)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Median = 31&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;there4; Median for the given data set is 31&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

questions.statement:
&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Let p, q and r be the mean, median and mode, respectively of the data given below:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;11, 12, 16, 3, 7, 9, 13, 16, 26, 23, 25, 19&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;What is the value of (p + 2q - r)?&lt;/span&gt;

questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Given:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Data :&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;11, 12, 16, 3, 7, 9, 13, 16, 26, 23, 25, 19&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Concept:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Median is the middle value when data is in asc. or desc. order.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Mode is the most repeated value in a data.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Formula:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(Mean = \frac{Sum\space of\space all\space observations}{Number\space of\space observations}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(if {\displaystyle }\space n\space is\space odd, {\displaystyle \mathrm {median} (x)=x_{(n+1)/2}}\\if {\displaystyle }\space n\space is\space even, {\displaystyle \mathrm {median} (x)={\frac {x_{(n/2)}+x_{(n/2)+1}}{2}}}\)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Mean = (11+12+16+3+7+9+13+16+26+23+25+19)/12&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;there4; Mean(p) = 15&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;After arranging data in asc. order,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Data : 3,7,9,11,12,13,16,16,19,23,25,26&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Median(q) = 14.5&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Mode(r) = 16&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;there4; p + 2q - r = 15 + 2&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 14.5 - 16 = 15 + 29 - 16 = 28.&lt;/p&gt;
